{"tid":1929274,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【救市政策】 美國今次大規模救市會有咩後果?","createTime":"2020-03-17T00:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T03:46:07.000Z","uid":351009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0ccd7621e616eed6fcfce700cd872cbdd0c4046d","tid":1929274,"uid":351009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:23:27.000Z","msg":"07/08金融海嘯始於美國樓市過熱，次按爆煲時引發信貸危機令金融機構骨牌式倒塌，導致全球經濟衰退<br />\n今次危機明顯由武漢肺炎引發，已經肯定嚴重影響中國、歐洲 (美國未必走得甩)<br />\n可以預見全世界實體經濟將會萎縮，已經高度分工嘅供應鏈受影響<br />\n<br />\n聯儲局已出嘅招:<br />\n0%利率<br />\n0% 存款準備金比率<br />\n$700 billion 量化寬鬆 (第一輪)<br />\n<br />\n可能會有嘅招數:<br />\nHelicopter money (Mitt Romney提出每人US$1000，輿論普遍支持)<br />\n行業bailout<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWYqs7U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwWYqs7U.png&h=07ee17e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔同嘅係危機前美國息率已經多年偏低，中國經濟本來已開始放緩<br />\n加上中美債務都越谷越大，大家點睇今次有咩後果?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cad6317cd9145a3d5477a064fedb8a1edd73626","tid":1929274,"uid":119897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:24:26.000Z","msg":"唔係救市 係救國"},{"pid":"5302cde2c6dfe1c9ac1e23d46d3abf8eba6dfee7","tid":1929274,"uid":107470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:27:13.000Z","msg":"Chinese virus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05dc8ebd1ee6cc87d32c016cf6412b92b12f5242","tid":1929274,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5302cde2c6dfe1c9ac1e23d46d3abf8eba6dfee7","tid":1929274,"uid":107470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:27:13.000Z","msg":"Chinese virus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T00:28:22.000Z","msg":"對準目標, 大力d打落去就係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b2e80d236822031c0f2605bbb3a8bf1495033b","tid":1929274,"uid":134415,"like":0